<!--pages/index/index.wxml-->

<image class='xx_bg' src='../../images/map_bg.jpg'></image>

<view class='deadline'>
    <view class='content'>
        <view>距离广西壮族自治区成立六十周年</view>
        <view>还有<label>50</label>天</view>
    </view>
</view>

<xx-map catchclick="clickTorch"></xx-map>



<view class='wall'>
    <image class="hero_he" src='../../images/hero_he.png' mode='widthFix'></image>
    <image class="hero_she" src='../../images/hero_she.png' mode='widthFix'></image>
    <view class='content'>
        <view class='editor' >
            <view class='title '>
                <view class="wall_title">南宁</view>
                <view class="wall_flex">
                    <!-- <image class="wall_icon" src="/static/images/my_select.png"></image> -->
                    <lable class="wall_zan">寻找 | 三娘湾</lable>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>

<view class='task'>
    <view class='content'>
        <view class='cover'>
            <image  src='../../images/swiper.jpg' mode='widthFix'></image>
        </view>
        <view class='summary'>
            <view class='des'>
            很久以前，那个时候的三娘湾还不叫三娘湾，人烟也非常稀少。那片海域只有苏、杨、李姓三个男青年，他们共同生活一条渔船上，共用一网同住一舱，日子...
            </view>
            <navigator url='/pages/article/article' class='more'>详情></navigator>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class='prize'>
        <view class='action'>
        <label>活动方式</label>：点击下方拍照按钮，上传您与刘三姐的合照，AI会自动判定所在景点
        </view>   
        <view class='result'>
            <label>奖励</label>：祝福积分、祝福卡
        </view>             
    </view>
            
</view>

<view style='height:60px;'></view>


<view class="menu">
    <!-- <view class="node" onclick="javascript: window.parent.location.href='/zfgx/bless/editor/'">
        <image src="../../images/menu_left.png"></image>
    </view> -->
    <view class="center" catchtap='toPainter' >
        <image src="../../images/menu_zan.png"></image>
        <label>识别祝福墙</label>
    </view>
    <view class="node" catchtap='onMap'>
        <image src="../../images/menu_right.png"></image>
    </view>
</view>





